          <p style="font-size:13px;color:#e0e0d8;line-height:1.65;margin-bottom:10px;"><strong style="color:#fff;">Name the scepticism explicitly.</strong> "It makes sense to be suspicious" outperforms "Juniper is different" — even though both make the same claim — because one earns credibility and one asserts it.</p>
