          <p style="font-size:13px;color:#e0e0d8;line-height:1.65;margin-bottom:10px;"><strong style="color:#fff;">Emotional universality over biography.</strong> Strip specific life circumstances. Keep emotional truths. The reader fills in their own story.</p>
